{{Quote|No such heresy will take place in the Solo Project. The process with Jacen Solo is precisely the opposite: he will remain fully human, yet acknowledge and proclaim the Truth. We will not have to alter or destroy him in any way. We merely demonstrate; he will do the rest himself.|[[Nom Anor]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Traitor">''[[The New Jedi Order: Traitor]]''</ref>}}
The '''Solo Project''' was the attempt, headed by [[Nom Anor]], by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] to break the will of [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] and convincing him into accepting the [[True Way]]. Theoretically, this would have allowed the Vong to hasten their conquest of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] by opening the way for 'peaceful' conversion of the rest of the population. However, with the help of [[Vergere]], Jacen not only thwarted the project's goals, but tricked his would-be masters into believing that he had accepted, only to then betray them by bonding with the [[World Brain]] of [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]] and using that bond to sabotage the [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongforming]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

